cascading.tuple

Class TupleEntryChainIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • cascading.tuple.TupleEntryIterator
      • cascading.tuple.TupleEntryChainIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterator<TupleEntry>

    public class TupleEntryChainIterator
extends TupleEntryIterator
    TupleEntryChainIterator chains the given Iterators into a single Iterator.

    As one iterator is completed, it will be closed and a new one will start.
